=80=9Cswami ji=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Cyour lordship.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p><p st=
yle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">SEBI alleged that the yogi had turned Ramkrishna in=
to a =E2=80=9Cpuppet,=E2=80=9D remotely controlling finances and steering p=
